## рҹҢҹ Overview

The **Student Fee One-Time Payment API** is a production-grade RESTful backend built for **LeedTech's Student Management Platform**. It enables students and administrators to process one-time fee payments, automatically calculates institution-provided incentive credits (matching program), updates student account balances in real time, and determines the next payment due date вҖ” all while processing payments securely through **Stripe**.

This project was designed and implemented as part of a **Full Stack Engineering Interview Exercise** and reflects real-world software engineering standards including clean architecture, domain modeling, validation, edge-case handling, and comprehensive test coverage.

