## рҹҢҗ API Endpoints

### рҹ”җ Authentication
| Method | Endpoint                          | Description              | Access        |
|--------|-----------------------------------|--------------------------|---------------|
| POST   | `/api/v1/auth/register`           | Register new user        | Public        |
| POST   | `/api/v1/auth/verify-otp`         | Verify OTP               | Public        |
| POST   | `/api/v1/auth/login`              | Login with credentials   | Public        |
| POST   | `/api/v1/auth/logout`             | Logout (clears cookies)  | Authenticated |
| POST   | `/api/v1/auth/magic-link/send`    | Send magic link          | Public        |
| POST   | `/api/v1/auth/google-login`       | Login with Google/Firebase | Public      |

### рҹ‘©вҖҚрҹҺ“ Student Management
| Method | Endpoint                              | Description                      | Access         |
|--------|---------------------------------------|----------------------------------|----------------|
| POST   | `/api/v1/students`                    | Create student profile           | ADMIN          |
| GET    | `/api/v1/students`                    | Fetch all students (paginated)   | ADMIN, TEACHER |
| GET    | `/api/v1/students/{id}`               | Fetch student by ID              | ADMIN, TEACHER |
| GET    | `/api/v1/students/number/{number}`    | Fetch by student number          | ADMIN, TEACHER |
| PUT    | `/api/v1/students/{id}`               | Update student profile           | ADMIN          |
| DELETE | `/api/v1/students/{id}`               | Soft delete student              | ADMIN          |
| GET    | `/api/v1/students/count`              | Count active students            | ADMIN          |
| GET    | `/api/v1/students/search`             | Search & filter (all properties) | ADMIN, TEACHER |
| GET    | `/api/v1/students/fee-defaulters`     | List fee defaulters              | ADMIN, ACCOUNTANT |
| GET    | `/api/v1/students/boarders`           | List boarders by hostel          | ADMIN          |
| GET    | `/api/v1/students/scholarships`       | List scholarship students        | ADMIN, ACCOUNTANT |

### рҹ’і Fee Payments
| Method | Endpoint                          | Description                         | Access                      |
|--------|-----------------------------------|-------------------------------------|-----------------------------|
| POST   | `/api/v1/one-time-fee-payment`    | Process one-time fee payment        | ADMIN, ACCOUNTANT, STUDENT  |

### рҹ“ё Profile Pictures
| Method | Endpoint                                      | Description              | Access |
|--------|-----------------------------------------------|--------------------------|--------|
| POST   | `/api/v1/students/{id}/profile-picture`       | Upload profile picture   | ADMIN  |
| DELETE | `/api/v1/students/{id}/profile-picture`       | Delete profile picture   | ADMIN  |

> рҹ“– **Full API documentation available at:** `http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html`

