## рҹ”җ Security & Authentication

This API implements a **multi-layer authentication strategy**:

### рҹ”‘ JWT Authentication
- Access token: **1 hour** expiry stored in `HttpOnly` cookie
- Refresh token: **7 days** expiry stored in `HttpOnly` cookie
- Tokens are **blacklisted in Redis** on logout

### рҹ”Ҙ Firebase Google Authentication
- Supports Google Sign-In via Firebase
- Firebase token verified server-side
- User auto-created if first login

### рҹ“§ OTP & Magic Link
- OTP hashed with **BCrypt** and stored in DB with expiry
- Magic link sent via **Mailtrap** with HTML email templates

### рҹ‘Ҙ Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)
- 27 roles supported: `ADMIN`, `SUPER_ADMIN`, `PRINCIPAL`, `ACCOUNTANT`, `CASHIER`, `STUDENT`, `TEACHER`, and more
- Each endpoint is protected by specific role combinations

---

## рҹ—„пёҸ Database Schema

### Flyway Migrations (in order)
| Version | File                                   | Description                    |
|---------|----------------------------------------|--------------------------------|
| V1      | `V1__create_users_table.sql`           | Users table + `user_role` enum |
| V2      | `V2__create_student_profiles_table.sql`| Student profiles + all enums   |
| V3      | `V3__create_payment_tables.sql`        | Student accounts + fee payments|

### рҹ’Ў Money Handling
> вҡ пёҸ All monetary values use `NUMERIC(19, 2)` in PostgreSQL and `BigDecimal` in Java.
> **Floating-point types (`double`, `float`) are never used for currency** to prevent precision errors.

---

## рҹ’і Stripe Payment Integration

### Payment Flow
```
Frontend (Angular)
    в”Ӯ
    в”ңв”Җ 1. Collect card details via Stripe.js Elements
    в”ңв”Җ 2. Create PaymentMethod вҶ’ receive paymentMethodId
    в””в”Җ 3. POST /one-time-fee-payment { studentNumber, paymentAmount, paymentMethodId, currency }
                в”Ӯ
                в””в”Җ Backend (Spring Boot)
                        в”ңв”Җ 4. Validate student + account
                        в”ңв”Җ 5. Calculate incentive + new balance
                        в”ңв”Җ 6. Calculate next due date
                        в”ңв”Җ 7. Create Stripe PaymentIntent
                        в”ңв”Җ 8. Confirm PaymentIntent with paymentMethodId
                        в”ңв”Җ 9. On success вҶ’ update balance + save FeePayment record
                        в””в”Җ 10. Return full payment response
```

### Stripe Test Cards
| Card Number          | Scenario              |
|----------------------|-----------------------|
| `4242 4242 4242 4242` | вң… Payment succeeds   |
| `4000 0000 0000 0002` | вқҢ Payment declined   |
| `4000 0025 0000 3155` | рҹ”җ Requires 3D Secure |

