## рҹҡҖ Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- вҳ• Java 21+
- рҹҗҳ PostgreSQL 15+
- рҹ”ҙ Redis (via WSL on Windows or Docker)
- рҹҗі Docker & Docker Compose (optional)
- рҹ”‘ Stripe account (test mode)
- вҳҒпёҸ Cloudinary account
- рҹ”Ҙ Firebase project
- рҹ“§ Mailtrap account

### 1. Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/asohyannick/studentFeeOneTimePayment.git
cd studentFeeOneTimePayment
```

### 2. Configure Environment Variables
Create a `.env` file in the project root (see [Environment Variables](#-environment-variables) section).

### 3. Start Redis (WSL)
```bash
# In WSL terminal
sudo service redis-server start

# Verify Redis is running
redis-cli -a yourpassword ping  # Should return PONG
```

### 4. Run the Application
```bash
# Build and run
mvn clean install
mvn spring-boot:run

# Or with a specific profile
mvn spring-boot:run -Dspring-boot.run.profiles=dev
```

### 5. Access Swagger UI
```
http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html
```

